      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel this way when the world feels so broken, but you're not alone in feeling this heavy burden. The fear of extinction is a powerful signal that something is wrong, and it's a valid reason to question our path. However, giving up on trying to build a future isn't the only option, and staying alive might be the only way to witness the changes that are happening.",
